{"tid":2517423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"電競玩家可成為真正的運動員　奧運首設5項電競賽事","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T10:12:47.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"683087b5a677bdec4c2cab86921178d77bfbefaa","tid":2517423,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:59:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/unwirehk/posts/10165474376655495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%2Fposts%2F10165474376655495&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=9bf84fe0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/unwirehk/posts/10165474376655495</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：<a href=\"http://UNWIRE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUNWIRE.HK&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=d025fca7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UNWIRE.HK</a><br />\n<br />\n電競玩家可成為真正的運動員~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Olympus-01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2FOlympus-01.png&h=7121bded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/05/03/international-olympic-committee-makes/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2Finternational-olympic-committee-makes%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=942054d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/05/03/international-olympic-committee-makes/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/2021-04-22-ovs-thumbnail-02-1280x725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F2021-04-22-ovs-thumbnail-02-1280x725.jpg&h=6a73d61e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際奧委會（IOC）日前正式宣佈，將設奧運虛擬系列賽Olympic Virtual Series，為首屆入加5項虛擬運動賽事的奧運，包括虛擬棒球、單車、賽車、賽艇及帆船。<br />\n<br />\n作為奧運項目的5個遊戲橫跨多個遊戲平台，包括Switch的《eBaseball 實況野球2020》、以手機平板連接單車的《Zwift》、用瀏覽器能玩的帆船比賽《Virtual Regatta》和 PlayStation上的賽車遊戲《Gran Turismo》，而划船賽事的遊戲未定，但可見遊戲相當多樣化，更令頂級玩家有機會成為真正的運動員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/AACXCA-694x386.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2FAACXCA-694x386.jpg&h=46c6e77d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/643x0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F643x0w.jpg&h=d2ce465a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/image-c-1680-565-694x233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2Fimage-c-1680-565-694x233.jpg&h=67078790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/i1cTINFCIx9aMEc-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2Fi1cTINFCIx9aMEc-694x390.jpg&h=ff7e4577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n奧運虛擬系列賽的賽期將為5月13日至6月23日，國際奧委會亦和相關五個國際體育聯合會合作，包括世界棒壘球聯合會、國際自行車聯合會、國際划船聯盟、世界帆船以及國際汽車聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n國際奧委會電競和遊戲聯絡小組（ELG）主席 David Lappartient 表示，各國正建立完善的虛擬體育計劃，十分欣賞是次國際奧委會和發行商之間的合作，他指「奧運虛擬系列賽是向虛擬體育世界和奧運，邁出令人振奮的一步」。"},{"pid":"bc2809be897cf6fa8f28ad388d7e3fdd7b764cc6","tid":2517423,"uid":1354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"加埋cso同跑online<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62c4368f219d4214751f55e48b266e808d1551c","tid":2517423,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"奧運真荒謬<br />\n看得自己那樣高<br />\n<br />\n人地唔洗你施捨都一早當係運動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班跟唔上時代既廢老"},{"pid":"955e3cad98c3523f37dadee96ede519c934553b9","tid":2517423,"uid":123189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"手指運動"},{"pid":"3ea7c5e6a5ad9adb6c87ffee058246b62962d944","tid":2517423,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"mon hunt點解唔計"},{"pid":"fa512e40e8d2f5389e070acca954e4fe3b32aaa2","tid":2517423,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"如果係以前機舖嗰種有架嘢畀你騎我都接受到....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}